Class InertEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.user.InertEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class InertEvent
extends java.util.EventObject
    This class represents a special EventObject which will be fired during the detection of a solution inertia. Only to be used with the InertEventListener.
    Author:
    Andréolli Cédric, Boulanger Chloé, Cléro Olivier, Guellier Antoine, Guilloux Sébastien, Templé Arthur
